title: Beautiful Bedroom! Hurry up! Never miss it!
posting_body: ['Beautiful affordable 1BD for rent.', 'Suitable for one college student or young working professional.', 'House conditions:', 'Large windows full of Bright light.', 'Hardwood floors.', 'Kitchen appliances: microwave, refrigerator, gas range, large sink and cabinets.', 'Washer/Dryer usage in the garage', 'High speed Internet with private, isolated WiFi Network', 'Nearby amenities:', 'CCSF(City College of San Francisco), SFSU(San Francisco State University)', 'Stonestown Shopping Center, Ocean Ave. with dining and entertainment spots', 'Transportation:', 'Mini bus line 54 (half block away) and metro line M(two blocks away)', '10-minute walk to Balboa Park Muni/Bart Station, which takes you less than 15 minutes to get to SF downtown by BART', 'Easy access to highway I-280 and US-101', 'Requirements:', '$1050 security deposit and first month rent', 'No pets.', 'No smoking.', 'No overnight guests.', 'No loud noise and parties.', 'At least 6 months lease is required.', 'Need clean, quiet and trouble-free person', 'Proof of fully COVID-19 vaccination record.', 'Contact: Brian']
